sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1520506
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: It is a gold ion detector. Gold ions will cause the CDS after PgolB to be expressed. PgolTS works like a constant promoter, producing gols which is inhibitor of Pgols. Once combining gold ions, gols will stop inhibitor PgolB. So, when there are gold ions, the CDS after this part will be expressed.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Wei wei
